  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The endoscopic thyroidectomy approach is gaining popularity in the surgical field. This
      registry tries to collect the outcomes including quality of life and complication for both
      endoscopic and conventional thyroidectomy methods.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
